issue.title: Development
issue.body:
This pull is the basic web server which is able to handle 2 routes and brings the person to the screen. The first screen with `localhost/` brings the user to the splashscreen aswell as the url `localhost/*`. If the user wants to access the hub / menu he has to utilize the url `localhost/menu` .
Everything seems to be stable and working.
